Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,ORIGINAL STORY BY: NATSU HYUUGA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}THIS STORY IS A FICION, AND ALL NAMES OF FIGURES ND ORGANIZATIONS ARE FICTITIOUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.59,0:01:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}MOREOVER, THE STORY HAS NO RELATION TO REAL-LIFE INCIDENTS AND EVENTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.82,0:01:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I heard that the palace woman who drowned and died killed herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,she was the maid for the Garnet Pavilion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who poisoned Lady Lishu at the garden party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she did it for her master, Concubine Ah-Duo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pure Concubine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.67,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was rumored that she'd be removed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.76,0:02:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from the four ladies and replaced by a younger concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Concubine Ah-Duo, at age 35,{\i} {\i1}is a year older than the Emperor.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She lost a boy that she had{\i} {\i1}when the Emperor was still{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Eastern Palace.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rear palace exists to have as many{\i} {\i1}children as possible. It can't be helped…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mother of a dead baby boy, huh?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Lady Lihua continues to not have{\i} {\i1}children, will she have the same fate?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.87,0:02:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Same with Lady Gyokuyou.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You never know for how long{\i} {\i1}she will be the Emperor's favorite.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even beautiful flowers will wilt one day.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flowers of the rear palace{\i} {\i1}must bear fruit to have value.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:03:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's leftovers from the tea party yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You have so many snacks that you have leftovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tea parties are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tea parties are duties{\i} {\i1}that concubines must fulfill.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Maomao, you get ready, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's another one?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone seems to be especially energized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Virtuous Concubine, Lady Lishu, is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The microcosm of the rear palace{\i} {\i1}can be found in this one room.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Concubine Lishu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poking at each other's hidden motives.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it the fate of all women to be on edge{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when facing other women?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honestly,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's more tense{\i} {\i1}than when the Emperor comes to visit.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Gyokuyou is gathering information{\i} {\i1}even in a friendly conversation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She may look gentle,{\i} {\i1}but she's still a concubine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She apparently sends{\i} {\i1}the information she collects back home.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her home is a resting point for trade,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so it must be important to understand{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the flow of people and the times.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The food taster at the garden party?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad she hadn't been punished{\i} {\i1}that harshly.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't bite, you know.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The other attendants aren't{\i} {\i1}paying attention to their lady at all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it doesn't seem{\i} {\i1}that they're bullying her for now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If my report to Sir Gaoshun was a mistake,{\i} {\i1}then that's great news.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't dislike sweets, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.86,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I love sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold, so I thought something like this would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I brewed citrus peels with honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll warm you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh? She can't have honey, either?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's being picky again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't even have what's offered to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Twitch, twitch.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Gyokuyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Ailan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we need to soak it a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll offer something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you have ginger tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unfortunately, it looks like{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the bullying rumors were true.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the cleaning up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You go rest, Maomao.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can clean up, you know.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:06:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the tea party with Concubines Gyokuyou and Lishu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought it was weird{\i} {\i1}to suddenly invite Lady Lishu{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.28,0:06:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for a tea party.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was his plan all along.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.41,0:06:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They seemed to enjoy themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.08,0:06:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not finished talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let me go?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,About the poisoning incident at the garden party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that it was done by the Garnet Pavilion maid that killed herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think she killed herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not for me to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a mere maid want to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,put poison on Lady Lishu the Virtuous Concubine's plate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you go help at the Garnet Pavilion starting tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:06:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Could you?"{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He says that,{\i} {\i1}as if I have any other choice.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A pavilion's atmosphere{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is determined by its master.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Gyokuyou's Jade Pavilion is homey,{\i} {\i1}and Lady Lihua's{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crystal Pavilion was{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}noble and refined.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.02,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the Garnet Pavilion{\i} {\i1}where Lady Ah-Duo lives is{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}efficient, elegant, and practical.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you come so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you for the next three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't been instructed by Sir Jinshi{\i} {\i1}to do anything.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Might as well work, then.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are those girls, Fengming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here to help with the spring cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank you for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Pure Concubine, Lady Ah-Duo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's neither flashy nor plump,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she's both feminine, masculine,{\i} {\i1}and dignified. She's beautiful.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So she's 35, huh?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she wore the robe, one could{\i} {\i1}mistake her for a young civil servant.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She might look better in hufu,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}rather than the robe and skirt{\i} {\i1}for concubines.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like they're into her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She reminds me of someone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Fengming, the head lady-in-waiting.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must come from a good family{\i} {\i1}based on her position,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she's very friendly.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,First, can you hang these books out to dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything is too heavy, just give it to a eunuch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As expected of a veteran{\i} {\i1}high-ranking concubine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though the mansion is clean,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it's packed with things.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Similar to the Jade Pavilion,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Garnet Pavilion attendants{\i} {\i1}are hard workers.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd like to show this to the ladies{\i} {\i1}who are all talk, no work.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finished here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You already got this much done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And everything is so neat. You're a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help at the reception room, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's friendly, observant,{\i} {\i1}and praises others well.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's skilled in employing others{\i} {\i1}as the head lady-in-waiting.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't done physical labor in a while.{\i} {\i1}I'm tired.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good work. Thank you for helping today. -Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're spending the night at the Garnet Pavilion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.11,0:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A sweet scent?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this. It'll be cold tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.29,0:10:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't been told by Sir Jinshi{\i} {\i1}to do anything,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would I really find the mastermind{\i} {\i1}behind the poisoning here?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone truly works hard.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not just the attendants, but…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Fengming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We can do the wiping down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just noticed it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Fengming is the leader of the pack.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.64,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's past the age to get married,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but if she had,{\i} {\i1}she would've been a good wife.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she not consider getting married?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe she chose to dedicate{\i} {\i1}her whole life to Concubine Ah-Duo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A strong sense of loyalty{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}could very well be the motive{\i} {\i1}for the poisoning.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that a new concubine may be coming,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Ah-Duo's position is at the{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}highest risk.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what if another seat opens up{\i} {\i1}before that?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Emperor only reacts positively{\i} {\i1}to ripened fruits.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As such, he does not visit Lady Lishu.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.47,0:11:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is great news,{\i} {\i1}considering her age of 14,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but she's also not fulfilling her duties{\i} {\i1}as a concubine.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the poison attempt was done{\i} {\i1}for Concubine Ah-Duo,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Lishu is a reasonable target.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can someone help here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Fengming's home runs a bee farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you have so much high-quality honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So the sweet scent yesterday was honey.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Lishu?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's only here with the food taster?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is she at the Garnet Pavilion?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, right. At the tea party…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all that happened at the Garnet Pavilion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else for me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what he's looking for,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm just a regular apothecary.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not my job to be a spy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyways, isn't he a little too laid back{\i} {\i1}these days?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me rephrase my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.67,0:13:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone were to use special methods to contact the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,who would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a mean question.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who could possibly do that is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,the head lady-in-waiting, Ms. Fengming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She had bandages wrapped around her left wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The colored wood tablet from before{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.53,0:13:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was wrapped around a woman's robe{\i} {\i1}with burnt sleeves.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone made the effort{\i} {\i1}to burn different colored flames.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the flames meant anything,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}it would be code.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honestly, I can't imagine{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a calm head lady-in-waiting like that{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}scheming anything like that, but…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's only my personal speculation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He took the chance to eat some honey.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.81,0:14:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure he knew this much.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.69,0:14:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to give treats to good girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-No thank you! -No need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need it. Do that for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.87,0:14:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just because he's good-looking,{\i} {\i1}he thinks he'd get away with anything!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the kind of pervert he was!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Gaoshun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll poison you with laxatives!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-You don't like sweets? -I like salt and spice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can eat it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shit. I can't get through to him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he wasn't a higher-up,{\i} {\i1}I would kick him in the crotch.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. I can't kick what's not there.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.06,0:14:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I just obey his orders,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}or run away and keep my dignity?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only if this was an aconite syrup…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.62,0:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You don't dislike sweets, do you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.12,0:15:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope you like it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honey?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Fengming's home
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-runs a bee farm. {\i1}-Lady Lishu?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Syrup…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Apothecary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing to my lady-in-waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.50,0:15:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Concubine Gyokuyou, this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose permission do you have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiaomao,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,he just got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.72,0:16:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you forgive Sir Jinshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you should lick him next time, Sir Gaoshun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lick? Well, that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a few things I need to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome… Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Jinshi isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Sorry for barging in like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.79,0:16:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What does a Jade Pavilion attendant need from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're from the garden party…{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you dislike honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever had an upset stomach from consuming honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's common to dislike a certain food after
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencing food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember. I was just a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hear my life was at risk at one point.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My wet nurse told me never to eat it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being quite rude. These are intrusive questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.31,0:17:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You didn't even protect your lady{\i} {\i1}at the tea party. You're one to talk.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to listen to an attendant like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's rude to you, Lady Lishu, the Pure Concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You should kick her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They must make outsiders{\i} {\i1}out to be the villain this way{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to make her think{\i} {\i1}they're her only friends.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-Lady Lishu… -{\i1}A sheltered rich girl like her{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}would easily get tricked.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An isolated concubine{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}must rely on her attendants.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.88,0:18:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't even realize{\i} {\i1}she's being bullied.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a vicious cycle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was ordered to come here. If you have
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,any complaints,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,say them directly to Sir Jinshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To Sir Jinshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should be able to get away{\i} {\i1}with this much.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm excited to think how these attendants{\i} {\i1}would approach that pervert eunuch.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Another question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever met Ms. Fegming,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the head lady-in-waiting at the Garnet Pavilion?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-Xiaomao? -Sir Gaoshun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,is there a way to learn about past events in the rear palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look in the court archives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What did she find out this time?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's a clever girl.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.03,0:19:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe that she's just 17.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's knowledgeable and calm.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She thinks things through rationally,{\i} {\i1}and can process information well.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She can be a bit strange,{\i} {\i1}but also somewhat impressive.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventeen years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,when the current Emperor was still the Eastern Palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he had a baby boy{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with Concubine Ah-Duo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The boy has since died.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The boy was born around the same time{\i} {\i1}as the Emperor's brother,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.57,0:19:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the child of the former Emperor{\i} {\i1}and the Empress Dowager.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:19:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He only had that one child{\i} {\i1}as the Eastern Palace.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.49,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His only concubine was Lady Ah-Duo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The current Emperor and Lady Ah-Duo are foster siblings,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so I get that he's attached to Lady Ah-Duo, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that lustful old man only had one concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby boy died 16 years ago. It was investigated by…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,LUOMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had imagined{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that this might be the case.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The medicinal herbs growing{\i} {\i1}in the rear palace{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are ones I've been using for a long time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone must have transported them here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A man who drags his foot{\i} {\i1}like an old woman.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A man so skilled in medicine{\i} {\i1}that it's a waste{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he's an apothecary{\i} {\i1}in the pleasure district.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A man with one of his knee bones removed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A former eunuch.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,LUOMEN
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:20:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW OF NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Next Episode, "Reducing Two to One."{\i}
